These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, balloon-flower, daisy
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person who growsdaisy##6
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
 8. the person who growsmarigold is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 9. the person who growszinnia is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
12. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
13. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Flower    | zinnia         | daisy     | balloon-flower     | marigold         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | writing    | sudoku     | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | cycling       | ice-hockey | volleyball | skiing       |

