 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person who growsazalea is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
 8. the person who growstulip is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8

