 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the train is not the person eating lemon##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
 9. the person eating lemon is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
10. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
