3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
4. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
7. the person eating lime is the person who growszinnia##1
8. the person eating lime is somewhere between the person who growslily and the person drinking fanta##7
9. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
