.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, magic-tricks, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: corn, cabbage, peas, raspberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, ship, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 2. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person eating peas##7
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating corn is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 7. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
 8. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
10. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
11. the person eating corn is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
13. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing    | magic-tricks | woodworking | fishing    |
| Food   | peas  | raspberry    | corn      | cabbage |
| Transport     | helicopter | car          | subway      | ship       |

