 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 2. the coach is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 3. the mechanic is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the coach is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the architect##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is the coach##1
 7. the bartender is not to the right of the coach##8
 8. the coach is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 9. the coach is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
10. the coach is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
11. the architect is not the person drinking iced-tea##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice     | milk  | iced-tea | almond-milk |
| Job           | bartender | coach | mechanic | architect   |
| Birthday   | april | january  | july   | may   |

