.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, russian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, rabbit, snake
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, musician, dressmaker, electrician
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the security-guard##1
2. the colombian is not to the right of the musician##8
3. the electrician is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the snake##2
4. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the colombian is not the dressmaker##6
6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the russian##1
7. the dressmaker is somewhere between the electrician and the musician##7
8. the electrician is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
9. the dressmaker is the canadian##1

